OL,5, An Israeli court has acquitted a border
OL,6, police officer charged with recklessly 
OL,7, killing an autistic Palestinian man in 
OL,8, occupied East Jerusalem in 2020.       
OL,10,FIyad Halaq, 32, was shot as he walked  
OL,11,Fto his special needs school. Police    
OL,12,Fsaid the unnamed officer thought he was
OL,13,Fcarrying a weapon and opened fire when 
OL,14,Fhe failed to obey orders to stop.      
OL,16,FThe Jerusalem district court found that
OL,17,Fthe officer "made an honest mistake".  
OL,19,FHalaq's mother condemned the verdict as
OL,20,F"a particular injustice".              
